BUGS:
    * Fixed invalid multiplication value for time in hours (duration) on
      utils.time_seconds(), long_processing_task, main_frame.cut_range()
      functions.

ADDED:
    * test implementation for test cases of some program features.
    * added useful progress information such as frame, fps, speed, bitrate
      and time remaining during conversion processes.


